import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"hello"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#hello"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Hello`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Check for the components that was used to did this challenge.`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
